            <div class="article abstract-view " itemprop="articleBody"><span class="highwire-journal-article-marker-start"></span><h1 id="article-title-1" itemprop="headline">Tandemly repeated genes promote RNAi-mediated heterochromatin formation via an antisilencing factor, Epe1, in fission yeast</h1>
               <div class="contributors">
                  <ol class="contributor-list" id="contrib-group-1">
                     <li class="contributor" id="contrib-1" itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope"
